videos.description: Bruins QB Josh Rosen connects with Darren Andrews down the left sideline for a 25-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCLA strikes first with Rosen's 25-yard TD

videos.description: Hawai'i's Metuisela 'Unga bowls over a Bruins defender to clear the way for Kaiwi Chung's 37-yard reception.
videos.headline: 'Unga lays vicious block on UCLA defender

videos.description: UCLA's Josh Rosen finds Theo Howard for a 26-yard touchdown, giving the Bruins a 14-0 lead.
videos.headline: Rosen tosses his 2nd TD of game

videos.description: Rainbow Warriors' QB Dru Brown rolls to his right and connects with Diocemy Saint Juste for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Play-action pass puts Hawai'i on the board

videos.description: Bruins' running back Demetric Felton takes a toss to the left and beats the defenders to the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Felton gets to the edge for UCLA TD

videos.description: The Bruins complete a double pass, from Josh Rosen to Caleb Wilson, then downfield to Nate Starks for a 39-yard pickup.
videos.headline: UCLA converts on trick play

videos.description: Josh Rosen continues his stellar play, connecting with Darren Andrews at the goal line for another Bruins touchdown.
videos.headline: UCLA's Rosen throws 3rd TD pass of first half

videos.description: Darnay Holmes intercepts the Hawai'i pass and returns it 30 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Bruins score on pick-six

videos.description: UCLA's QB Josh Rosen throws his fourth touchdown pass of the day, and his third to Darren Andrews, this time from 34 yards out.
videos.headline: UCLA's Andrews scores 3rd TD of day on pass from Rosen

videos.description: Hawai'i's Dru Brown dumps it off to John Ursua who takes it in 2 yards to score the touchdown.
videos.headline: Rainbow Warriors' Ursua finds the end zone

videos.description: UCLA's Bolu Olorunfunmi takes the handoff and converts the goal line carry to put UCLA up 49-14.
videos.headline: Bruins pound it in from 1 yard out

videos.description: Caleb Wilson makes an impressive grab over the Hawai'i defender to catch Josh Rosen's fifth touchdown of the day.
videos.headline: Rosen throws back-shoulder pass for 5th TD of game

videos.description: Diocemy Saint Juste makes a cut and finds an opening for a huge Rainbow Warriors gain.
videos.headline: Hawai'i's Saint Juste breaks off 66-yard scamper

videos.description: Backup Bruins QB Devon Modster doesn't see the rush and is sacked by KK Padello for a safety.
videos.headline: UCLA sacked in end zone for safety

videos.description: Rainbow Warriors' backup QB Cole McDonald shows off some impressive speed, eluding defenders en route to a huge gain.
videos.headline: Hawai'i freshman QB rips off 58-yard run

videos.description: Freshman QB Cole McDonald scrambles it in from eight yards out for a Hawai'i touchdown.
videos.headline: Hawai'i QB McDonald uses his legs to score
